{"id": "1333421118312157295", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "때리는거, 중독, 반격, 광기 폭발 등등 전부.", "timestamp": "2025-01-27T12:59:28.372000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1333421202001236021", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "계역정통은 파티가 어떤 경계인가에 따라서 효과가 다릅니다.", "timestamp": "2025-01-27T12:59:48.325000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1333421258993434654", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "제가 쓰는 혼돈의 경우, 은열쇠 게이지 상승폭이 더 커짐.", "timestamp": "2025-01-27T13:00:01.913000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1333421338831884310", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "248331431103692802", "author_name": "gojwannam", "author_bot": false, "content": "아 그런 효과를 가진거였군요?", "timestamp": "2025-01-27T13:00:20.948000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1333421494016933971", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "248331431103692802", "author_name": "gojwannam", "author_bot": false, "content": "거의 2주 했는데 효과를 지금 처음앎..", "timestamp": "2025-01-27T13:00:57.947000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1333421527538073631", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "크리티컬 확률, 크리티컬 데미지는 파티원 개개인마다 따로 적용됨.", "timestamp": "2025-01-27T13:01:05.939000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1333421644408033351", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "물론 창조물 같은걸로 버프를 받는 크확, 크뎀은 전체 적용이고.", "timestamp": "2025-01-27T13:01:33.803000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1333421936071413824", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "", "timestamp": "2025-01-27T13:02:43.341000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1333421935698382858", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 4147540, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1300659495550062592/1333421935698382858/image.png?ex=6a373833&is=6a35e6b3&hm=e19e4250aac8b6d80c9e321ade67f2d9ffebdbf1f297632aebe8e781d8a40dd2&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1333421955415806054", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "여기 ? 누르면 설명 나옵니다.", "timestamp": "2025-01-27T13:02:47.953000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1333422274052620290", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "248331431103692802", "author_name": "gojwannam", "author_bot": false, "content": "저거도 보면서 비밀계약을 잘 넣어야 겟네요", "timestamp": "2025-01-27T13:04:03.922000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1333422394316161188", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "서포터들도 올리면 올리는 만큼 전체 딜량 올라가는거니까.", "timestamp": "2025-01-27T13:04:32.595000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1333422458484555837", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "3,5,6번 파츠 주옵은 피해강효로 하는게 무난할겁니다.", "timestamp": "2025-01-27T13:04:47.894000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1333422538998415371", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "물론 다른거 올려야하는 컨셉이 확고한 캐릭이라면 다른거 해야겠지만요", "timestamp": "2025-01-27T13:05:07.090000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1333422731089154088", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "그리고 저 팀정보 4개 외에는 개별 적용입니다. 광기획득이나 은열쇠게이지획득이나.", "timestamp": "2025-01-27T13:05:52.888000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1333423324428238889", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "248331431103692802", "author_name": "gojwannam", "author_bot": false, "content": "웬만ㅇ해서 3,5,6 을 피해강효 해주고 딜러는 크리나 크리뎀 서폿은 계역정통이나 죽음저항으로 껴주면 되는걸까요?", "timestamp": "2025-01-27T13:08:14.351000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1333423482331070485", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "서폿은 계역정동, 광기획득, 은열쇠게이지획득, 죽음저항..... 글쎄요. 덱이 어떤 지점을 지향하는가에 따라서 전부 달라지겠죠.", "timestamp": "2025-01-27T13:08:51.998000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1333423591802409041", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "248331431103692802", "author_name": "gojwannam", "author_bot": false, "content": "음.. 그렇군요..", "timestamp": "2025-01-27T13:09:18.098000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1333423602804199505", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "가령 지금 제 캐릭들 보이시죠?", "timestamp": "2025-01-27T13:09:20.721000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1333423650090516480", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "저기서 라모나는 은열쇠 게이지 상승에 올인했습니다.", "timestamp": "2025-01-27T13:09:31.995000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1333423724749258824", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "명륜 2개가 은열쇠 게이지 상승량 만큼 매턴 자동으로 공급하는 구조임.", "timestamp": "2025-01-27T13:09:49.795000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1333423840839073882", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "레이크는 크리확률. 크리를 일으키면 은열쇠게이지 얻고, 스킬도 크리가 터지면 이득보는 구조라서임.", "timestamp": "2025-01-27T13:10:17.473000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1333423959747858493", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "가렌은 광기획득. 광기폭발을 빨리 돌릴수록 컴퓨팅파워를 더 빨리 돌릴수 있어서임.", "timestamp": "2025-01-27T13:10:45.823000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1333424060943831111", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "타비는 크뎀. 명륜이 기본적으로 크확을 많이 올려주기때문에 크확에는 그다지 손을 안썼습니다.", "timestamp": "2025-01-27T13:11:09.950000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1333424225742229564", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "248331431103692802", "author_name": "gojwannam", "author_bot": false, "content": "게임이 신경써야하는게 생각보다 많네요", "timestamp": "2025-01-27T13:11:49.241000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1333424433305489418", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "저도 제가 하는게 정답이라고 확신 못합니다. ㅋ", "timestamp": "2025-01-27T13:12:38.728000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1333424625450877060", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "248331431103692802", "author_name": "gojwannam", "author_bot": false, "content": "명륜도 전부 보라색 쓰는게 아니라 파랑 명륜도 쓰는걸 보니 전부 돌파해놔야 할것 같고..", "timestamp": "2025-01-27T13:13:24.539000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1333424920981405707", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "248331431103692802", "author_name": "gojwannam", "author_bot": false, "content": "급하게 할 필요가 없는걸 아는데 쉽지 않네요", "timestamp": "2025-01-27T13:14:34.999000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1333425047326556223", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "248331431103692802", "author_name": "gojwannam", "author_bot": false, "content": "이번에 소레엘 복각했던데 데려갈만 할까요?", "timestamp": "2025-01-27T13:15:05.122000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1333425115794243584", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "저도 한달 약간 넘은 초짜라서 혼돈만 계속 쓰다보니.", "timestamp": "2025-01-27T13:15:21.446000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1333425139819479150", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "혈육쪽은 거진 모릅니다. ㅋ", "timestamp": "2025-01-27T13:15:27.174000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1333425200527708225", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "이번에 버프 먹어서 나쁘진 않은거 같던데.", "timestamp": "2025-01-27T13:15:41.648000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1333425729706262589", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "단지 소레엘은 딜러니까, 만약 드실거라면 명함만 뽑는건 비추입니다.", "timestamp": "2025-01-27T13:17:47.814000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1333425780444762184", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "뽑을거라면 돌파를 해야해요. 최소3돌, 가능하면 초한돌파까지.", "timestamp": "2025-01-27T13:17:59.911000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍉", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1333428705841643521", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "248331431103692802", "author_name": "gojwannam", "author_bot": false, "content": "딜러는 최소 3돌...", "timestamp": "2025-01-27T13:29:37.380000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1333428795872645172", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "248331431103692802", "author_name": "gojwannam", "author_bot": false, "content": "그냥 다음가챠 노려야겠네요 ㅋㅋㅋ", "timestamp": "2025-01-27T13:29:58.845000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
